@startuml
object Teacher
object StudentController
object SendStudentMessagesUseCase
object StudentReaderFunctions
object DiscordRecipientResolver
object DiscordMessenger
object ClassDiscordController
object SendChannelPostUseCase
object RecipientData <<database>>
Teacher --> StudentController : 1: send DM request
StudentController --> SendStudentMessagesUseCase : 2: execute
SendStudentMessagesUseCase --> StudentReaderFunctions : 3: load recipient bases
StudentReaderFunctions --> RecipientData : 4: SELECT students/classes
SendStudentMessagesUseCase --> RecipientData : 5: load identities and class guilds
SendStudentMessagesUseCase --> DiscordRecipientResolver : 6: resolve guild member
SendStudentMessagesUseCase --> DiscordMessenger : 7: send direct message
SendStudentMessagesUseCase --> StudentController : 8: delivery summary
Teacher --> ClassDiscordController : 9: channel post request
ClassDiscordController --> SendChannelPostUseCase : 10: execute
SendChannelPostUseCase --> RecipientData : 11: load class binding
SendChannelPostUseCase --> DiscordMessenger : 12: send channel message
@enduml
